    "description": "Color Lim 是一款平台冒险游戏，讲述一个名叫 Lim 的小粘液在一个颜色决定一切的世界里寻找自己颜色的旅程。在这个废墟城市与自然交织的世界里，Lim 吸收了各种颜色，开辟了一条新路。Lim 能否找到自己真正的颜色？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/8558c823f506c724d36d2dd156285223.poster.avif?t=1767614896\" width=642 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/8558c823f506c724d36d2dd156285223.webm?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/8558c823f506c724d36d2dd156285223.mp4?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > [唤醒色彩的力量] </h2>没有自己的颜色，Lim 吸收并转换周围的颜色，将它们变成强大的工具。在与根据颜色变化的敌人互动的过程中，规划你的战略，让每时每刻都充满新的挑战和机遇。体验由你的选择所塑造的无限可能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/bc4cc05fc7d3ae17c20bc001a6588258.poster.avif?t=1767614896\" width=642 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/bc4cc05fc7d3ae17c20bc001a6588258.webm?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/bc4cc05fc7d3ae17c20bc001a6588258.mp4?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > [多样的路径，独特的故事] </h2>废弃的城市、长满藤蔓的街道和隐藏的谜团正等待着你。Lim 面对各种环境，选择无数条道路，克服挑战，开启新的可能性。与 Lim 一起探索这个充满色彩的世界吧！你会选择哪条路呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/fb3d965e0ff52806e278bcc62fd43311.poster.avif?t=1767614896\" width=642 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/fb3d965e0ff52806e278bcc62fd43311.webm?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/fb3d965e0ff52806e278bcc62fd43311.mp4?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > [现实与幻想的结合] </h2>这里曾经是一个繁荣的文明，如今却被大自然接管。在这个既熟悉又陌生的世界里，Lim 拯救了与世隔绝的人，并重建了一个村庄。每当有新的人到来，村庄就会成长和变化，小小的希望再次绽放。你会在这里发现什么秘密呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/896bbdea5ac44dfc5be6841fb2ec411f.poster.avif?t=1767614896\" width=642 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/896bbdea5ac44dfc5be6841fb2ec411f.webm?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244430/extras/896bbdea5ac44dfc5be6841fb2ec411f.mp4?t=1767614896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
